      <title>Aramco削减了全球最大的股息，以打击沙特预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/aramco-cuts-world-s-biggest-dividend-in-blow-to-saudi-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿兰科（Aramco）削减了世界上最大的股息，这对沙特阿拉伯的预算赤字扩大，因为该公司试图释放自己的财务压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/aramco-cuts-world-s-biggest-dividend-in-blow-to-saudi-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 06:10:47 GMT</pubDate>
