      <title>特朗普绘制红线以阻止中国贬值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-draws-currency-red-line-for-pboc-with-manipulation-talk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对中国货币政策的评论正在加强中央银行的案子，即使面对迫在眉睫的贸易战，也要坚持其保持人民币稳定的战略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-draws-currency-red-line-for-pboc-with-manipulation-talk</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 03:57:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当投资者评估关税响应时，中国股票减少损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/chinese-stocks-fall-as-tariff-reality-outweighs-stimulus-hopes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者认为该国对唐纳德·特朗普的关税的回应，中国股票的下降幅度下降了，这使人们对贸易紧张局势的全面升级升级的任何直接担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/chinese-stocks-fall-as-tariff-reality-outweighs-stimulus-hopes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 01:39:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金持有贸易战争前景的收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/gold-holds-gain-as-trump-stokes-haven-buying-with-tariff-moves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国对特朗普政府的关税政策进行报复之后，黄金稳定了，加深了对全球贸易战争的前景的关注，这可能会增加对避风港资产的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/gold-holds-gain-as-trump-stokes-haven-buying-with-tariff-moves</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 00:26:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
